txt.en: 'I am Gísil, Thane of Garsfeld. I have fought against the foes of Rohan through all of my life... Orc, Dunlending, Haradrim - none have escaped my spear! My elder brother, Dagred, had long been Reeve of these lands until he was felled by the arrow of an Orc and now his son, Fastred, rules Snowbourn in his stead. I have grown weary with the King's decline, and pray that he will return to his old ways soon, lest the Mark be the worse for it.'
